channel.title: Adding stuff from one server to another
channel.description:
ok so i want to add something from one server to another. so like dungeoneering for this one server http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,492527.0.html and all its things and details in it to another 317 server HELP :S
edit: details in it theres a box that gives you money in there, you can buy items from shop like primal and stuff (idk how to get that into the other server) and theres like a bridge connecting to the other side and when you die you dont lose anything you start at bridge again. and when you leave the place you leave all the items and you get points. way confusing! and there is a dungeoneering.class and a .java for your guys's info when i type search dungeoneering all this comes . dungeoneering.class,dungeoneering.java,client.java,actionhandler.java,clickingbuttons.java,config.java,combatassistant.java,playerassistant.java,npchandler.java
